Package: CNNregR
Type: Package
Title: R Interface for CNNreg Cell Type Deconvolution
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Xue Wang, Yuanhang Liu
Maintainer: Xue Wang <wang.xue@mayo.edu>
Authors@R: c(
    person("Xue", "Wang", email = "wang.xue@mayo.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Yuanhang", "Liu", email = "liu.yuanhang@mayo.edu", role = "aut"))
Description: Provides R functions for preprocessing scRNA-seq and bulk RNA-seq data for CNNreg deconvolution analysis. Includes gene selection, quality filtering, reference generation, and wrapper functions to run CNNreg deconvolution from R.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
